con:testCase.name: GoodCase-DEV-Reporting-FullUseCase
con:testCase.con:description:
Based on requirements in us: https://www.sg.de.o2.com/jira/browse/DRC-3683
Followed test-scenario is implemented:
Load topup data from core server DB to Abstimmmodul DB - verify data Import EDR data to Abstimmmodul DB - verfify data Match topup and EDR data Import payment data for ATM and Mipay topups Reconcile topup and payment data - verfify result Generate SAP postings for topups and payments
The following payment channels need to be tested with min. one topup:
ATM
POS
Mipay
Remittance
Manual Topups
Acceptance criteria:
Use of the output of one process step as input for the following process step is verified by tests.

con:config.con:query: insert into TRANSLOG ( TRANSFER_SEQ_ID, TRANSFER_TBL, SRC_START, SRC_END, SRC_END_MESSAGE, SRC_ROWS) values ( TRANSLOG_SEQ.nextval, 'edr_data', to_date('${Run TestCase-getDate#outDate}', 'dd-MM-yyyy HH24:MI:SS'), to_date('${Run TestCase-getDate#outDate}', 'dd-MM-yyyy HH24:MI:SS'), 'done', 15)
SELECT * From reporting_topup order by media_type, topup_id DESC

con:configuration.query: SELECT topup_id, msisdn,partner, amount/100 amount, media_type, reconciliation_id, matching_id, to_char(COMMITTED_DATE, 'yyyy-MM-dd') bookDT, to_char(COMMITTED_DATE, 'dd-MON-yyyy HH24:MI:SS') edrDate From reporting_topup --where media_type in (23, 40) AND matched=1 order by media_type, topup_id DESC

con:config.con:query: insert into EDR_DATA (EDR_ID, EDR_RECORD_ID, EDR_SEQ_ID, EDR_DATE, EDR_TYPE, EDR_RESULT, EDR_SP_ID, EDR_MSISDN, EDR_VOL_TYPE, EDR_ASSIGNED_AMOUNT, EDR_MEDIA_TYPE, EDR_EVENT_COST, EDR_BALANCE, EDR_VOUCHER_NO, EDR_CORRELATION_ID, EDR_TOPUP_ORIGIN, EDR_VOUCHER_SERIAL_NO, TRANSFER_SEQ_ID, STATUS, ERROR_CODE, CREATED_DATE, LAST_CHANGED_DATE, LAST_CHANGED_USER_ID) values (EDR_DATA_SEQ.nextval, 302, ${#Project#Random8}, to_Date('${Data Source-getTopups-forEDR#edrDate}','dd-MON-yyyy HH24:MI:SS'), 4, 0, '${#TestCase#edr_SP}', '${Data Source-getTopups-forEDR#msisdn}', 4, ${Data Source-getTopups-forEDR#amount}, ${Data Source-getTopups-forEDR#media_type}, null, 3${#Project#Random3}, null, '${Data Source-getTopups-forEDR#matching_id}', '${#TestCase#edr_topup_orig}', null, '${JDBC Request-getMaxID#ResponseAsXml#//Results[1]/ResultSet[1]/Row[1]/MAXTRANSFER_SEQ_ID[1]}', 0, null, systimestamp, systimestamp, '${#Project#Tester}')
